<p><strong>The WHATWG mailing lists are no longer active.</strong></p>

<p>Discussions now happen on the repositories for the individual
<a href="https://spec.whatwg.org/">standards</a>, and
<a href="https://github.com/whatwg/meta">whatwg/meta</a> can be used for issues without a logical
home.</p>

<h3>Archives</h3>

<p>A static archive is available at <a href="https://lists.whatwg.org/">lists.whatwg.org</a>.</p>

<p>A separate <a href="https://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/public-whatwg-archive/">whatwg@whatwg.org
archive</a> is also maintained by the W3C, and this archive is searchable.</p>

